# .toolignore Template

This template generates .toolignore files to tell KontextMind which files to skip.

## Files to Always Ignore

- `.git/` - Git repository
- `node_modules/` - npm/yarn/pnpm dependencies
- `venv/` / `.venv/` - Python virtual environments
- `dist/` / `build/` - Build output
- `coverage/` - Test coverage
- `vendor/` - Composer/vendor dependencies
- `.env` / `.env.*` - Environment files with secrets

## Secrets to Ignore

- `*.pem` - Private keys
- `*.key` - Key files
- `*.crt` - Certificate files
- `credentials.json` - Credentials files
- `secrets/` - Secrets directory

## Other

- `*.min.js` - Minified JavaScript
- `.DS_Store` - macOS metadata
- `.cache/` - Cache directories
- `tmp/` / `temp/` - Temporary files